headline: CSX Corp. Announces Date for Second Quarter Earnings Release and Earnings Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., June 25, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) will release second quarter financial and operating results after the market close on Wednesday, July 23, 2025. This will be followed by a conference call and live webcast hosted by the company’s management team at 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time.
